      <abstract>
        <p>Testimony of Ota Klinger, which became a part of the Documentation campaign, Prague.
          Klinger describes the fate and death of his fellow prisoner Jan Herrmann during the air
          strike of the allies on the Schwarzheide camp.</p>
      </abstract>


